9563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2944547/org/d17e445c2372ea99595eea7fb909a402.jpg/E35q0bCv9CrUKbQAzXgXQlVvbYq1buKLepDB3nqQwd4?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2944547%2Forg%2Fd17e445c2372ea99595eea7fb909a402.jpg%2FE35q0bCv9CrUKbQAzXgXQlVvbYq1buKLepDB3nqQwd4%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=87d63bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32c7e47ae9d8f617578fa275dbe53910a01a2e7","tid":1322753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】傳有O記探員被示威者淋偈油<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1528435/即時-港聞-逃犯條例-傳有O記探員被示威者淋偈油\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1528435%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%89O%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%A2%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%8B%E5%81%88%E6%B2%B9&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=dbe95860\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1528435%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%89O%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%A2%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%8B%E5%81%88%E6%B2%B9&h=7113615e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1528435/即時-港聞-逃犯條例-傳有O記探員被示威者淋偈油</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190621/_2019062123414294216.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190621%2F_2019062123414294216.jpeg&h=f9e1d6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在大批示威人士包圍警總期間，一名Ｏ記探員欲剪斷封門索帶時，遭人「突襲」淋潑偈油，衣衫及手腳沾滿油迹，被逼退回總部，警方發言人稱正就事件了解。<br />\n<br />\n警察總部被數以千計示威者包圍，無論正門和側門所有出入口，俱被鐵馬鐵欄堵塞，部分更被人綁上索帶。消息稱，警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科（Ｏ記）一名探員，一度拿着鐵鉗衝往堵路處，圖將索帶剪斷，卻遇到噓聲和反抗，有人更向他潑淋偈油。<br />\n<br />\n探員衣衫及手腳沾滿點點油迹，立即撤回，有同袍為他拍照存檔拍下證據，並向上級報告，而事件則在網上及警察社文群組流傳。警方發言人稱，就上述傳出的消息，正加以了解。"},{"pid":"228d46843a4f31920c83dc97b62fbfd7253c2fae","tid":1322753,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32c7e47ae9d8f617578fa275dbe53910a01a2e7","tid":1322753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】傳有O記探員被示威者淋偈油<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1528435/即時-港聞-逃犯條例-傳有O記探員被示威者淋偈油\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1528435%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%89O%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%A2%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%8B%E5%81%88%E6%B2%B9&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=dbe95860\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1528435%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%89O%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%A2%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%8B%E5%81%88%E6%B2%B9&h=7113615e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1528435/即時-港聞-逃犯條例-傳有O記探員被示威者淋偈油</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190621/_2019062123414294216.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190621%2F_2019062123414294216.jpeg&h=f9e1d6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在大批示威人士包圍警總期間，一名Ｏ記探員欲剪斷封門索帶時，遭人「突襲」淋潑偈油，衣衫及手腳沾滿油迹，被逼退回總部，警方發言人稱正就事件了解。<br />\n<br />\n警察總部被數以千計示威者包圍，無論正門和側門所有出入口，俱被鐵馬鐵欄堵塞，部分更被人綁上索帶。消息稱，警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科（Ｏ記）一名探員，一度拿着鐵鉗衝往堵路處，圖將索帶剪斷，卻遇到噓聲和反抗，有人更向他潑淋偈油。<br />\n<br />\n探員衣衫及手腳沾滿點點油迹，立即撤回，有同袍為他拍照存檔拍下證據，並向上級報告，而事件則在網上及警察社文群組流傳。警方發言人稱，就上述傳出的消息，正加以了解。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-